    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Within the wikification the table of content and the child pages are sorted per name.
But they should always be presented in the order they are written in the docu.</p>

<p>Example:
Within Zend_Measure the chapters are not sorted as expected. They seem to be thrown together.</p>

<p>Instead of Introduction -&gt; Writing -&gt; Creation</p>

<p>it displays Introduction -&gt; Creation -&gt; Edit</p>

